departure facilitated--

13:58.004 --> 14:01.940
which means "led to"--
a breakthrough with Cleveland.

14:01.942 --> 14:03.441
I think giving him
a little freedom

14:03.443 --> 14:05.476
might actually
solidify your bond.

14:05.478 --> 14:07.278
Are you sure?
But I thought...

14:07.280 --> 14:08.947
Do not argue
with the man!

14:08.949 --> 14:10.014
He's a doctor,
kinda!

14:10.016 --> 14:11.349
Thank you.

14:11.351 --> 14:12.684
We'll see you
in a week.

14:12.686 --> 14:13.918
(door opens, closes)

14:15.688 --> 14:17.021
