before you cash that check.

14:20.226 --> 14:22.961
Wait 20 minutes before
you go into that bathroom.

14:33.572 --> 14:35.240
Cleveland,
you've been bouncing

14:35.242 --> 14:36.407
on that trampoline
for three hours.

14:36.409 --> 14:38.676
Donna, what has Dr. Nerse

14:38.678 --> 14:41.246
been telling us
the past few sessions?

14:41.248 --> 14:43.514
(sighs) To support
your inner child,

14:43.516 --> 14:45.984
because your
father never did.

14:45.986 --> 14:47.418
Right.

14:47.420 --> 14:49.053
Jordan! Ah!

14:49.055 --> 14:50.154
Say it, say it.

14:50.156 --> 14:51.422
Swish.

14:51.424 --> 14:52.557
There it is!

14:52.559 --> 14:53.658
(bottles clinking)

14:53.660 --> 14:55.593
Morning, sir.

14:55.595 --> 14:59.664
