15:02.535 --> 15:03.668
But I only had
one or two treats.

15:03.670 --> 15:06.170
Your wastebasket
disagrees, sir.

15:07.873 --> 15:09.941
(crying):
I have a problem!

15:09.943 --> 15:11.709
Well, here's another one.

15:11.711 --> 15:14.245
$1,300.89?!

15:14.247 --> 15:15.880
That's ridiculous!

15:15.882 --> 15:17.048
How am I going
to pay for that?!

15:17.050 --> 15:18.683
No idea.

15:18.685 --> 15:21.619
Of course,
I'd stop eating if I were you.

15:22.688 --> 15:23.888
Right, right, stop eating.

15:23.890 --> 15:26.524
Oh, who am I kidding?

15:26.526 --> 15:29.060
I'm in the 'Blerone Zone.

15:29.062 --> 15:30.828
But this is it.
I swear.

15:33.465 --> 15:36.067
How are you doing that?

15:36.069 --> 15:37.268
(screams)

15:37.270 --> 15:38.102
(laughs)

15:38.104 --> 15:41.639
(panting)

15:44.310 --> 15:46.511
Why can't I quit you?

15:48.447 --> 15:50.048
(groans)

15:52.952 --> 15:54.919
Dr. Nerse, this is
how he dressed

15:54.921 --> 15:56.120
for my niece's baptism
yesterday.

15:56.122 --> 15:57.889
Jesus is a
Cowboys fan.

15:57.891 --> 16:00.558
Jesus loves soccer!

16:00.560 --> 16:02.493
Donna, Cleveland is correct.

16:02.495 --> 16:03.795
Jesus is a Cowboys fan.

16:03.797 --> 16:06.497
Thank you, Dr. Nerse.

16:06.499 --> 16:07.966
Wait in the car, Donna.

16:07.968 --> 16:09.500
The men need to talk.

16:12.338 --> 16:13.938
(door opens, closes)

16:13.940 --> 16:15.807
Doc, you're a miracle worker.

16:15.809 --> 16:17.475
Eh, I'm glad you're happy
with the results, Cleveland.

16:17.477 --> 16:20.812
But I'm afraid there's
been a price increase.

16:20.814 --> 16:22.413
Whatever it is,
I'll pay it.

16:22.415 --> 16:24.816
What'd it go up
to? 101, 103?

16:24.818 --> 16:26.985
It's gone up to coming over
Saturday night

16:26.987 --> 16:28.753
and sleeping with my wife.

16:28.755 --> 16:30.521
I beg your
you-got-to-be-(beep)-me?

16:30.523 --> 16:33.157
My wife has always wanted
to have sex with a black man.

16:33.159 --> 16:34.759
And like most Jews,
I only know one black person.

16:34.761 --> 16:37.128
And that's you.

16:37.130 --> 16:38.763
You know, Doc,
I think my marriage

16:38.765 --> 16:40.098
is feeling all better now.

16:40.100 --> 16:41.766
So, this will be all...

16:41.768 --> 16:44.135
If you don't sleep
with my wife,

16:44.137 --> 16:45.703
I'll have no choice
but to tell Donna

16:45.705 --> 16:47.005
you bribed me.

16:47.007 --> 16:47.972
(gulps)
I see.

16:47.974 --> 16:50.375
Let me ask you,
Cleveland,

16:50.377 --> 16:53.011
how would that
make her feel, hmm?

16:53.013 --> 16:55.313
Happy or sad?

16:55.315 --> 16:56.714
Sad.
That's right.

16:56.716 --> 16:57.515
So, you'll do
what I say.

16:57.517 --> 17:00.284
Okay.

17:00.286 --> 17:03.621
(whimpering)

17:03.623 --> 17:05.323
(snoring)

17:05.325 --> 17:07.825
(whimpering)

17:07.827 --> 17:09.794
(snoring)

17:09.796 --> 17:14.132
(whimpering)

17:14.134 --> 17:15.366
(snoring)

17:15.368 --> 17:18.002
Now, be careful,
I got pancakes in there.

17:18.004 --> 17:19.537
Absolutely, ma'am.

17:19.539 --> 17:20.905
I'll bring them
up to your room

17:20.907 --> 17:22.874
after you settle in.

17:22.876 --> 17:23.674
I hope you're
here to pay me.

17:23.676 --> 17:25.810
I am.

17:25.812 --> 17:27.645
But I'm not paying with money.

17:27.647 --> 17:28.146
I'm paying with the law!

17:29.715 --> 17:34.218
It's says,
"Not for resale."

17:34.220 --> 17:35.253
(gulps)

17:35.255 --> 17:36.587
Rallo Tubbs,
you're guilty of

17:36.589 --> 17:38.856
over 1,200 counts
of reselling a food item

17:38.858 --> 17:41.325
that is not for resale.

17:41.327 --> 17:42.660
You'll never get me!

17:44.329 --> 17:46.264
(grunting)

17:48.000 --> 17:49.600
Please, Junior,
I'll do anything.

17:49.602 --> 17:51.769
Just don't turn me in,
I can't go back.

17:51.771 --> 17:55.106
Everything about me
is much too pretty.

17:55.108 --> 17:57.675
All right,
but under one condition.

17:57.677 --> 17:59.110
You name it.

17:59.112 --> 18:00.845
Give me full custody
of the fridge,

18:00.847 --> 18:03.614
erase all my debt, and
shave one of those fake parts

18:03.616 --> 18:05.716
in your Afro like
Arnold Drummond had.

18:05.718 --> 18:06.284
Who?
Gary Coleman!

18:08.253 --> 18:09.954
Wow.

18:09.956 --> 18:12.156
All that sadness,
and now forgotten.

18:15.627 --> 18:18.229
Oh, my God, I can't
(whistle) my therapist's wife!

18:18.231 --> 18:22.900
But my therapist won't let me
not (honk) my
therapist's wife!

18:22.902 --> 18:26.037
What if you
just lightly (steam
whistle) her (cat screeching)?

18:26.039 --> 18:27.705
Not even that.

18:27.707 --> 18:30.141
I made a vow never
to cheat on Donna.

18:30.143 --> 18:33.377
Although, what if
I rewrote the vows?

18:33.379 --> 18:34.479
Been down that road.

18:34.481 --> 18:36.047
Landed you in treatment.

18:36.049 --> 18:37.482
Gabriel Byrne. David Byrne.

18:37.484 --> 18:38.616
Burning down the house.

18:38.618 --> 18:39.951
<i>Bringing Down the House.</i>

18:39.953 --> 18:41.619
Queen Latifah. Queen.
Freddy...

18:43.956 --> 18:45.590
Much better.

18:45.592 --> 18:48.326
Look, the reason Donna
took you to counseling

18:48.328 --> 18:50.061
was to save
your marriage.

18:50.063 --> 18:51.162
And now the only way
to save your marriage

18:51.164 --> 18:53.097
is to sleep
with this woman.

18:53.099 --> 18:57.001
Cleveland, unlike the
gays, you have no choice.

18:57.003 --> 18:58.769
Lester!

18:58.771 --> 19:01.806
They did not give us this
platform to spread ignorance.

19:01.808 --> 19:05.610
But for Donna's sake,
I will not
spend the night or cuddle.

19:05.612 --> 19:08.880
Oh, who am I kidding?
I'm a cuddler.

19:11.483 --> 19:13.151
Now, Cleveland,
my wife isn't looking

19:13.153 --> 19:14.952
for anything
kinky or weird.

19:14.954 --> 19:17.455
Can I do it with my
underwear and tube socks on?

19:17.457 --> 19:19.257
Yeah, however
you guys do it.

19:22.094 --> 19:23.060
WOMAN:
You're late.

19:24.129 --> 19:25.663
I like that.

19:25.665 --> 19:26.430
It's authentic.

19:26.432 --> 19:27.398
Thank you.

19:34.106 --> 19:35.640
(moaning)

19:35.642 --> 19:37.775
(grunts)
What am I doing?!

19:37.777 --> 19:41.012
I, Cleveland Brown,
love my wife.

19:41.014 --> 19:42.513
But even more than that,

19:42.515 --> 19:43.981
I respect her.

19:43.983 --> 19:46.150
And I will not
be unfaithful to her

19:46.152 --> 19:48.619
as long as we both shall live.

19:48.621 --> 19:52.623
I will no longer lie to her,
nor will I lie with you.

19:52.625 --> 19:54.358
Nor be on my knees,

19:54.360 --> 19:56.928
nor assume any type
of wheelbarrow position.

19:58.163 --> 20:00.965
I am a happily married man.

20:00.967 --> 20:03.968
And a pretty happy guy.

20:03.970 --> 20:06.370
And that's therapy.

20:06.372 --> 20:09.407
And those are the vows
I wanted to hear.

20:09.409 --> 20:11.242
Dr. Nerse, Donna!

20:11.244 --> 20:13.010
What are you doing
in this bedroom?!

20:13.012 --> 20:14.912
Are you sleeping
with the therapist

20:14.914 --> 20:16.047
to save our marriage?

20:16.049 --> 20:18.149
Oh, Donna.

20:18.151 --> 20:19.817
No, Cleveland,
don't you see?

20:19.819 --> 20:21.986
This was all a scheme
so that you'd realize

20:21.988 --> 20:23.754
your true feelings
for Donna.

20:23.756 --> 20:25.590
Well, how about that.

20:25.592 --> 20:27.558
It took you longer than
most patients.

20:27.560 --> 20:30.328
Most men feel too guilty
to pay a bribe

20:30.330 --> 20:32.363
to gain a tactical advantage
in their marriage.

20:32.365 --> 20:34.165
What?
Not me.

20:34.167 --> 20:36.400
I knew you would never
betray me, Cleveland.

20:39.871 --> 20:44.208
Does your wife want to
have sex with a black  <i>woman?</i>

20:44.210 --> 20:46.410
(laughter)

20:46.412 --> 20:48.412
We had a lot
of fun tonight,

20:48.414 --> 20:51.282
but there's nothing funny
about marriage counseling.

20:51.284 --> 20:52.783
It's a waste of
everyone's money

20:52.785 --> 20:56.687
and they always
side with the wife.

20:56.689 --> 20:58.990
Happy Valentine's Day,
everybody!
